SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT 0 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 UNION SELECT 1 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':1' UNION SELECT 2 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':2'

SELECT PRD007.PRD_DAT, PRD007.MTOCD, PRD007.COL_CD, PRD007.COLI_CD, PRD007.PRD_LIN, PRD007.EFM, PRD007.PRGRES, PRD007.M_AFPLN, PRD007.M_AFOFF, PRD007.M_VQOFF, PRD007.M_PAKING, PRD007.M_SHPNG, PRD007.M_RTN, PRD007.M_RSHPNG, PRD007.M_EXOUT, PRD007.STK_NVQ, PRD007.STK_VQ, PRD007.STK_PAK, PRD001.CTEGRY FROM PRD007, PRD001 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':1' AND SUBSTR (PRD007.MTOCD,1,1) <> '3' AND (PRGRES<>0 OR M_AFPLN<>0 OR M_AFOFF<>0 OR M_VQOFF<>0 OR M_PAKING<>0 OR M_SHPNG<>0 OR M_RTN<>0 OR M_RSHPNG<>0 OR M_EXOUT<>0 OR STK_NVQ<>0 OR STK_VQ<>0 OR STK_PAK<>0) AND PRD007.MTOCD = PRD001.MTOCD ORDER BY EFM, PRD001.CTEGRY, MTOCD, COL_CD, COLI_CD

SELECT PRD007.PRD_DAT, PRD007.MTOCD, PRD007.COL_CD, PRD007.COLI_CD, PRD007.PRD_LIN, PRD007.EFM, PRD007.PRGRES, PRD007.M_AFPLN, PRD007.M_AFOFF, PRD007.M_VQOFF, PRD007.M_PAKING, PRD007.M_SHPNG, PRD007.M_RTN, PRD007.M_RSHPNG, PRD007.M_EXOUT, PRD007.STK_NVQ, PRD007.STK_VQ, PRD007.STK_PAK, PRD001.CTEGRY FROM PRD007, PRD001 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':1' AND SUBSTR (PRD007.MTOCD,1,1) = '3' AND (PRGRES<>0 OR M_AFPLN<>0 OR M_AFOFF<>0 OR M_VQOFF<>0 OR M_PAKING<>0 OR M_SHPNG<>0 OR M_RTN<>0 OR M_RSHPNG<>0 OR M_EXOUT<>0 OR STK_NVQ<>0 OR STK_VQ<>0 OR STK_PAK<>0) AND PRD007.MTOCD = PRD001.MTOCD ORDER BY EFM, PRD001.CTEGRY, MTOCD, COL_CD, COLI_CD
